---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Arun Setty" description="Developer, philosopher, builder. Learn more about who I am.">
  <!-- Cinematic version -->
  <section class="hero-section cinematic-only">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-label">About</span>
      <h1 class="gradient-text page-title">About Me</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cinematic-only">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-content">
          <p>
            I'm a fullstack developer and product architect with a passion for building
            beautiful, scalable, and performant web applications. I think deeply about
            the systems that shape our world — both technical and philosophical.
          </p>

          <p>
            Currently, I'm building the core product at
            <a href="https://brokenatom.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Broken</a>,
            a no-code platform that empowers anyone to create structural applications
            from scratch. Before that, I worked across companies like
            <a href="https://www.hotstar.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hotstar</a>,
            <a href="https://www.foxsense.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Foxsense</a>,
            and several AI startups.
          </p>

          <h2>Education</h2>
          <p>
            I graduated from the
            <a href="https://www.iitb.ac.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Indian Institute of Technology, Bombay</a>
            with a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science and Engineering. IIT Bombay
            is where I fell in love with both the rigour of computer science and the
            breadth of philosophical thinking.
          </p>

          <h2>Philosophy</h2>
          <p>
            I believe the best software comes from understanding people, not just
            technology. Every system we build is a reflection of how we think about
            the world. I'm drawn to questions about consciousness, systems thinking,
            and the ethics of the tools we create.
          </p>
          <p>
            My approach to building is influenced by stoic philosophy — focus on what
            you can control, build with intention, and always ask whether what you're
            building genuinely serves the people who'll use it.
          </p>

          <h2>Beyond Code</h2>
          <p>
            When I'm not in front of a computer, I'm probably reading, driving,
            writing, or sleeping. I'm passionate about open source software and
            contributing to the developer community.
          </p>

          <div class="about-links">
            <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="glass-card about-link">
              Resume &rarr;
            </a>
            <a href="/journey" class="glass-card about-link">
              My Journey &rarr;
            </a>
            <a href="/writing" class="glass-card about-link">
              My Writing &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terminal version -->
  <section class="hero-section terminal-only">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-label">About</span>
      <h1 class="gradient-text page-title">$ cat about.md</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="terminal-only">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="terminal-file">
        <div class="terminal-file-header">
          <span class="terminal-comment">---</span>
          <br/>
          <span class="terminal-key">name:</span> <span class="terminal-val">Arun Setty Kodavali</span>
          <br/>
          <span class="terminal-key">role:</span> <span class="terminal-val">Fullstack Developer & Product Architect</span>
          <br/>
          <span class="terminal-key">location:</span> <span class="terminal-val">India</span>
          <br/>
          <span class="terminal-key">education:</span> <span class="terminal-val">IIT Bombay — B.Tech CSE</span>
          <br/>
          <span class="terminal-comment">---</span>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-section">
          <span class="terminal-heading">## current</span>
          <p class="terminal-text">
            Building the core product at <a href="https://brokenatom.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Broken</a> — a no-code platform that empowers anyone to create structural applications from scratch. Before that, worked across <a href="https://www.hotstar.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hotstar</a>, <a href="https://www.foxsense.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Foxsense</a>, and several AI startups.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-section">
          <span class="terminal-heading">## education</span>
          <p class="terminal-text">
            Graduated from <a href="https://www.iitb.ac.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Indian Institute of Technology, Bombay</a> with a Bachelor's in Computer Science and Engineering. Where I fell in love with both the rigour of CS and the breadth of philosophical thinking.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-section">
          <span class="terminal-heading">## philosophy</span>
          <p class="terminal-text">
            The best software comes from understanding people, not just technology. Every system we build is a reflection of how we think about the world. Drawn to questions about consciousness, systems thinking, and the ethics of the tools we create.
          </p>
          <p class="terminal-text">
            Influenced by stoic philosophy — focus on what you can control, build with intention, and always ask whether what you're building genuinely serves the people who'll use it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-section">
          <span class="terminal-heading">## beyond_code</span>
          <p class="terminal-text">
            When not in front of a computer: reading, driving, writing, or sleeping. Passionate about open source software and contributing to the developer community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-links">
          <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="glass-card about-link">
            ./resume.pdf
          </a>
          <a href="/journey" class="glass-card about-link">
            ./journey/
          </a>
          <a href="/writing" class="glass-card about-link">
            ./writing/
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-eof">
          <span class="terminal-comment">// EOF</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding-top: 140px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .page-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }

  .about-content a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 48px 0 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .about-link {
    padding: 10px 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* Theme visibility toggling */
  .terminal-only { display: none; }

  :global([data-theme="terminal"]) .cinematic-only { display: none; }
  :global([data-theme="terminal"]) .terminal-only { display: block; }

  /* Terminal file styles */
  .terminal-file {
    max-width: 700px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .terminal-file-header {
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.15);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .terminal-comment {
    color: #009922;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .terminal-key {
    color: #00cc33;
  }

  .terminal-val {
    color: #00ff41;
  }

  .terminal-section {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .terminal-heading {
    color: #00ff41;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.3);
  }

  .terminal-text {
    color: #00cc33;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .terminal-text a {
    color: #00ff41;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .terminal-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.15);
  }

  .terminal-eof {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1);
  }
</style>
